OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FBrightest in the southeast,
OL,6,Fwith some sunny spells here. Cloudier
OL,7,Fin the northwest and some southern
OL,8,Fcoastal districts, with periods of
OL,9,Fmostly light rain, easing later. Warm
OL,10,Fand rather humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FMostly fine with some sunshine.
OL,14,FTurning increasingly hot and humid
OL,15,Ftowards the weekend, staying mainly
OL,16,Fdry, but with the possibility of
OL,17,Fthunderstorms on Friday and Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
